text: Rajab Ali Fakir is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-2. ==Career== Fakir was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-2 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Rajab Ali Fakir
